---
const pageTitle = "About Glowing Body";
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';    
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
const identity = {
  firstName: "Sarah",
  country: "Canada",
  occupation: "Technical Writer",
  hobbies: ["photography", "birdwatching", "baseball"],
};
---

<Header />

<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">{pageTitle}</h1>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">At Glowing Body, we believe that true wellness starts from within. We're passionate about empowering you with knowledge about the food that fuels your body and mind.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">What We Offer</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li>Real Food Wisdom: Understanding whole, unprocessed foods</li>
                <li>Brain Food Insights: Nutrients that power your cognitive function</li>
                <li>Food Science: Latest research and innovations in nutrition</li>
                <li>Mindful Eating: Building a conscious relationship with food</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Our Commitment</h3>
            <p>We're dedicated to bringing you evidence-based information about nutrition, helping you make informed decisions about what you consume. From ancient wisdom to cutting-edge food science, we're here to guide you on your journey to optimal health.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Join Our Journey</h2>
        <p>Discover how the right nutrients can transform your body and mind. Let's explore the fascinating world of conscious nutrition together, one bite at a time.</p>
    </section>
</main>

<Footer />